Who we are
We aim to be at the forefront of innovation, charting the path to meaningful learning experiences in support of a future-ready Public Service. You will be joining a collaborative team that supports CSC’s ongoing efforts to innovate and incubate new learning methods for impactful learning experiences in the Public Service.

We work with internal and external partners to identify future learning trends and develop prototypes and pilots for&nbsp;potential application in CSC. This supports the organisation’s efforts to scale impactful learning innovation across the Singapore Public Service.

Job Description

  Collaborate with peers and partners to apply and drive best-practice learning experience design and align learning programmes with expected business outcomes.
  Apply best-practice UX and UI design approaches to rapidly create proof-of-concepts, wireframes, UX flows and interactive prototypes.
  Stay current with trends on leading science and technology innovation and learning science and draw out implications on design.
  Review learning analytics and learner feedback, and provide recommendations for learning experience improvements.
  Analyse performance data to determine performance and learning objectives that deliver expected business results.
